sequenceDiagram
    participant User as Data Scientist
    participant Browser as Web Browser
    participant Dashboard as ODH Dashboard<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS1.2+
    participant OAuth as OpenShift OAuth<br/>HTTPS/443
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>HTTPS/6443 TLS1.2+
    participant NotebookCtrl as Notebook Controller
    participant Notebook as Notebook Pod<br/>StatefulSet
    participant KServe as KServe Controller
    participant ODHModel as ODH Model Controller
    participant InferenceService as InferenceService Pod<br/>Model Server
    participant S3 as S3 Storage<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS1.2+
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>Metrics Collection

    %% Workflow 1: Launch Notebook
    rect rgb(220, 240, 255)
        note over User,Notebook: Workflow 1: Launch Jupyter Notebook
        User->>Browser: Access ODH Dashboard
        Browser->>OAuth: Authenticate (OAuth 2.0)
        OAuth-->>Browser: OAuth Token
        Browser->>Dashboard: GET / (Bearer Token)
        Dashboard-->>Browser: Display Notebook Images
        User->>Browser: Select Image + Configure Resources
        Browser->>Dashboard: POST /api/notebooks<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        Dashboard->>K8sAPI: Create Namespace (if needed)<br/>mTLS Client Cert
        Dashboard->>K8sAPI: Create Notebook CR<br/>mTLS Client Cert
        K8sAPI-->>NotebookCtrl: Watch Event: Notebook Created
        NotebookCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create StatefulSet<br/>mTLS Client Cert
        K8sAPI->>Notebook: Schedule Pod
        Notebook->>S3: Pull Workbench Image<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS1.2+
        NotebookCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create Service + Route<br/>mTLS Client Cert
        User->>Browser: Access notebook-{name}.apps.{cluster}
        Browser->>Notebook: HTTPS/443<br/>OAuth Proxy Auth
        Notebook-->>Browser: Jupyter Interface
    end

    %% Workflow 2: Model Training to Deployment
    rect rgb(240, 255, 220)
        note over User,S3: Workflow 2: Model Training to Deployment
        User->>Notebook: Train Model Locally
        Notebook->>S3: Save Model Artifacts<br/>HTTPS/443 AWS IAM/S3 API
        User->>Browser: Create InferenceService
        Browser->>Dashboard: POST /api/inferenceservices<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        Dashboard->>K8sAPI: Create InferenceService CR<br/>mTLS Client Cert
        K8sAPI-->>KServe: Watch Event: InferenceService Created
        K8sAPI-->>ODHModel: Watch Event: InferenceService Created
        KServe->>K8sAPI: Create Knative Service/Deployment<br/>mTLS Client Cert
        ODHModel->>K8sAPI: Create OpenShift Route<br/>mTLS Client Cert
        ODHModel->>K8sAPI: Create Istio VirtualService<br/>mTLS Client Cert
        ODHModel->>K8sAPI: Create ServiceMonitor<br/>mTLS Client Cert
        K8sAPI->>InferenceService: Schedule Predictor Pod
        InferenceService->>S3: Download Model Artifacts<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS1.2+ (Storage Initializer)
        S3-->>InferenceService: Model Files
        InferenceService->>InferenceService: Load Model into Memory
        User->>Browser: POST /v1/models/model:predict<br/>to {isvc}.apps.{cluster}
        Browser->>InferenceService: HTTPS/443 TLS1.2+<br/>via Route/Istio
        InferenceService-->>Browser: Prediction Result (JSON)
        InferenceService->>Prometheus: Expose /metrics<br/>HTTP/9090
        Prometheus->>InferenceService: Scrape Metrics<br/>HTTP (ServiceMonitor)
    end

    %% Workflow 3: Distributed Training with Kueue
    rect rgb(255, 240, 220)
        note over User,Prometheus: Workflow 3: Distributed Training with Job Queueing
        User->>Notebook: Submit PyTorchJob CR
        Notebook->>K8sAPI: Create PyTorchJob<br/>mTLS Client Cert
        K8sAPI-->>Kueue: Watch Event: PyTorchJob Created
        Kueue->>Kueue: Evaluate Queue + Quota
        Kueue->>K8sAPI: Admit Workload<br/>mTLS Client Cert
        K8sAPI->>TrainingOp: Unsuspend PyTorchJob
        TrainingOp->>K8sAPI: Create Master/Worker Pods<br/>mTLS Client Cert
        K8sAPI->>TrainingPods: Schedule Pods
        TrainingPods->>TrainingPods: Distributed Training<br/>Framework Protocol (TCP/29500)
        TrainingPods->>S3: Save Model Artifacts<br/>HTTPS/443 TLS1.2+
        TrainingPods->>Prometheus: Expose Training Metrics
    end

    participant Kueue as Kueue Controller
    participant TrainingOp as Training Operator
    participant TrainingPods as Training Pods<br/>Master + Workers
